title: Kendall Jenner Flashes Boobs While Topless in Shower Stall
text:
Comments In one of the snaps, the 19-year-old model gives a sharp gaze to the camera and leans against the wall while putting her arms in such a way to cover her nipples. 
Kendall Jenner went for another semi-nude photo shoot when she's in Paris. The " Keeping Up with the Kardashians " star bared her top and flashed her boobs in a sexy photo shoot with photographer Mert Alas. The photographer took to Instagram on Thursday, October 8 to share two steamy snaps of Kendall. In one of the snaps, the 19-year-old model gave a sharp gaze to the camera and leaned against the wall while putting her arms in such a way to cover her nipples. Her hair looked wet and her eye makeup ran down her face. "Wash away her sins[.] KENDALL in paris @kendalljenner #parisisburning," read the caption. The other snap showed the runway beauty standing under the shower. Kendall's facial expression suggested that she felt refreshed. Posting the latter snap on her Instagram page, she captioned it, "Washing away my sins." It's unclear whether the shots would be used as part of an upcoming magazine or they just took them as impromptu snaps. Another user @gizkaysworld commented, "She so beautiful." Addressing Kendall's curves, user @rafaela_lais said, "Body goals." User @jendall4life, similarly, wrote, "She is hot." However, there were some Instagram users who focused on the caption of the snaps. User @almightyprophet wrote, "Her spirit and soul is still dirty." Another user @44hafiz44I also said, "Dont like sinners." User @zahrakamali12 even wrote, "She accepted thinks her sins are gone by posting this."
